## Javascript

- document.getElementByID
- document.querySelector; to select the class
- pass value from function to another function
- array
- Math.random()*3; to randomize the choices (*3 is for 3 choices) => Math.random() will give answer between 0-1, therefore \*3 will give 0-3
- Math.floor(Math.random()\*3); Math.floor will give only the integer that does not include decimal regardless of high/low decimals
- switch statement
- switch (.... + ....); case: "..+.." action.. break;
- classList.add; add class to HTML tag
